title: Andrew Darwin
text: I am a third-year undergraduate student at the University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA) pursuing a major in Statistics and Data Science with a minor in Data Science Engineering. When I’m not analyzing data or coding, you’ll find me playing video games, experimenting with photography, or playing volleyball. I love strategy-based games, capturing unique moments through my camera, and staying active on the court.
